19 CONTRIBUTORY DEATH BENEFIT NOT SUBJECT TO OVERPAYMENT OFFSETS
20 SECTION 1.2.(a) G.S. 135-9(b) reads as rewritten:
21 "(b) Notwithstanding any provisions of law to the contrary, any overpayment of benefits
22 or erroneous payments to a member in a State-administered retirement system or the former
23 Disability Salary Continuation Plan or the Disability Income Plan of North Carolina, including
24 any benefits paid to, or State Health Plan premiums or claims paid on behalf of, any member or
25 beneficiary who is later determined to have been ineligible for those benefits or unentitled to
